print.simulation

Class Client

  • java.lang.Object
    • print.simulation.Client

  • public class Client
extends java.lang.Object
    Client.java A class representing a print task with specific job size in pages and a particular service rate at which it can be serviced. 
        Project: print.simulation
    Platform: jdk 1.6.0_14; NetBeans IDE 6.8; Mac OSx
    Course: CS 143
    Hours: 2 hours
    Created on May 25th, 2013, 10:00:00 PM
    See Also:
    Server, PrintSimulationGUI, Queue, Random
